Creating Lists

You can create ordered and unordered lists in Markdown.

Unordered List

  • Item 1
  • Item 2
    • Subitem 2.1
    • Subitem 2.2
  • Item 3

Ordered List

  1. First item
  2. Second item
  3. Third item

Lists help organize information clearly!
